Whatever Kylie, Kim, Khloe and Kourtney can do - Kendall Jenner can do even better. 
The 21-year-old Keeping Up With The Kardashians star just took a leaf out of her sisters' extensive sexy selfie collections to post her own eye-popping picture. 
With her face just out of view, the brunette poses in a pair of high-waisted black bottoms which she seductively hitches up on one side. 
Her enviably flat tummy is on full display as she snaps the shot with her other hand. 
"Chaos," she cheekily captioned it. Kendall and Kylie pose with Caitlyn over the Christmas holidays (Photo: KingKylie/snapchat) 
Her raunchy post comes after she revealed the most upsetting rumours she's heard about herself involved speculation she'd undergone cosmetic surgery. 
The supermodel fired back at her critics after she came under fire for an appearance on her sister Kylie's live stream in November, with some fans claiming she had larger lips and fuller cheeks. Kendall also recently posted this sexy CK snap (Photo: Instagram @kendalljenner)
